    "htmlContent": "Find your best partner... Lemon\nLemon is a chat app for anyone who wants to find a best partner!\nYou can use this app for free and it’s easy to register!\n\n【Recommend for those who...】\n・can’t believe they can meet their match.\n・are bored.\n・are always with same friends\n・want to meet new people but do not have the opportunity\n・have nothing to do\n\n【How to use】\nYou only need a nickname to register!\nYou can immediately start talking and find your favorite person.\n\nIf you are interested in this app, feel free to use it!^^\n\n【Should not be used to】\n・Slander or attack on any individual or group of individuals.\n・Talk about job openings and solicitation.\n・Transmit your personal information.\n\n【Considerations】\nThis App is not available for under 18 years old.\nPlease don’t tell others your SNS IDs.\n\n【Link for Privacy of advertisement】\nhttps://m.facebook.com/ads/ad_choices\n\n【Cancellation policy】\nPlease note that we do not accept the cancellation for the current month subscription.\n\n【Terms and conditions】\nhttps://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/lemonchat/static/terms-lemon-en.html\n\n【Privacy Policy】\nhttps://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/lemonchat/static/privacy-policy-lemon-en.html",
